{
  "texts": [
    "LLMs have long been known to encode and perpetuate bias, including stereotypes (Bender et al., 2021b).",
    "LLM mirror their training data that reflects the historical injustice and under-representation present in most data sources (Weidinger et al., 2021a).",
    "To address these issues, a significant portion of crowd intelligence (a.k.a.",
    "RLHF (Christiano et al., 2017a)) used in LLM training is allocated to steering them toward safe generations (OpenAI, 2023).",
    "LLMs are trained to mirror certain ethical, moral, and social values."
  ]
}